[[File:CH_cow_2.jpg|thumb|Sac.]]

'''Sac''' ([[Ingiriis]]: Cow) waa [[xoolo]] [[gurijoog]] ah oo [[dad]]ku dhaqdaan. Sacu waa [[dhedig]]a [[lo']]da, halka [[dibi]]gu yahay [[lab]]ka.

Sacu wuxuu ka mid yahay [[xayawaan]]ka [[naasley]]da ah ee ilmahooga nuujiya. Lo'da dhedig waxay leeyihiin [[naas|4 naasoo]] oo [[caano]] fiican laga helo, kuwaas oo loo isticmaalo siyaabo badan sida in la cabo, laga sameeyo [[subag]], burcad, yoghurt iwm. 
Wadanada qaar, gaar ahaan dalalka saboolka ah, waxaa laga sacaha loo isticmaalaa in [[beer]]aha lagu qoto, wax lagu jiito, iyo la rartbo

Isku soo duuboo, [[lo']]du waxay quudisaa shacabka aduunka ayadoo [[hilib]]kooda oo la cuno. 

Wakhti laga joogo 10,500 oo sano, ayaa lo'da lagu dhaqan jirey koonfurbari dalka [[Turkiga]]. Intaas oo [[qarni]] oo ka dambeeysay lo'du waxay ku faafeysay dunida. In ka badan [[bilyan|1.3 bilyan]] oo lo' ah ayaa maanta ku nool daafaha dunida. 

Guud ahaan, lo'du waa xoolo muhiim u ah [[dad|aadamaha]] ayagoo laga helo [[hilib]] uu nafaqo ka helo [[jidh]]ka dadku, [[dhogor]] laga sameeyo [[dhar]]ka, xadhkaha iwm. 
Intaas waxaa dheer, [[saxaro|saxarada]] [[xoolo|xoolaha]] laga helo waxaa lagu nafaqeeyaa [[caro|carada]].

